{"tid":528884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅嘉良拒現身無綫頒獎禮","createTime":"2018-01-14T10:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T10:09:09.000Z","uid":128369,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8c36c29168cd064ed690ebd052f83a7f715e9f","tid":528884,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"無綫去年11月《萬千星輝賀台慶》本邀請羅嘉良（撈家）出席，豈料他答應後，無綫卻因為數萬元機票及酒店費用而叫停，令撈家極度不滿，事後無綫高層余詠珊就解釋是時間配合不到，並非預算問題。<br />\n不過，昨日有周刊報道指無綫近日竟再出手邀三屆視帝撈家，出席本月21日舉行的《萬千星輝頒獎典禮》，因撈家憑《與諜同謀》一劇與王浩信、陳豪及馬國明等爭奪視帝寶座，但他表示要在內地趕劇而婉拒。報道中又指無綫稍後播映由撈家主演、愛奇藝與寰亞合拍的劇集《無間道》，由於撈家跟該劇監製梁家樹感情深厚，所以日內將返港幫手宣傳。記者昨向撈家了解，對於缺席頒獎禮，他透過微信說：「係呀，因為時間唔啱，度唔到期。《無間道》係好早之前同我度㗎，所以度到囉。」"},{"pid":"b882e515d8689c64cc94cd42e9c5ec85cde60a80","tid":528884,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"俾套咁既野要佢拍"},{"pid":"a942514161e60d7196a0317ccab2432befc87b0f","tid":528884,"uid":127988,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"算膠數啦 ,  tvb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44e7580fc6b15b9578c218d3193874460253cba","tid":528884,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"肯定冇獎 去黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da61584cab8b530e287de955f07c5800c938bc28","tid":528884,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T18:25:18.000Z","msg":"睬你都有味"},{"pid":"a1b1f5e657e6622f6ed9690ac6e16fdb42f72031","tid":528884,"uid":9263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"出席都得個坐字，<br />\n去黎托咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982785cda0c4cabe9fc7870733bd4b63c5880775","tid":528884,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"攞左三次再拎有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a70165fcb858caf2b79d8cb4d5786dca42a08c5","tid":528884,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"事後無綫高層余詠珊就解釋是時間配合不到，並非預算問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當人傻的嗎, 如果個期唔啱，人地ㄧ早拒絕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}